<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0156a" xml:id="I01.0061.0156a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0156a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 61</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0156a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>趙郡王高叡修定國寺頌</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0156a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0156a0101">□□齊天保八年歲次丁
<lb ed="I" n="0156a02" type="honorific"/>丑四月己巳朔八日丙子。
<lb ed="I" n="0156a03" type="honorific"/>使持節都督定瀛幽滄安
<lb ed="I" n="0156a04" type="honorific"/>平東燕七州諸軍事撫軍
<lb ed="I" n="0156a05" type="honorific"/>將軍儀同三司定州刺史
<lb ed="I" n="0156a06" type="honorific"/>六州大都督趙郡王高叡。
<lb ed="I" n="0156a07" type="honorific"/>地居兩<note n="0156001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30482"/>＝獻【史】</note><note n="0156001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30482"/>【佛拓】，獻【史】</note><app n="0156001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">獻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30482"/></rdg></app>。化凝二南。六度
<lb ed="I" n="0156a08" type="honorific"/>是宣。十善無滯。比丘僧琴。
<lb ed="I" n="0156a09" type="honorific"/>業重行高。栖玄宅妙。同捨
<lb ed="I" n="0156a10" type="honorific"/>異珍。建斯靈宇。<note n="0156002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虬＝虯【史】</note><note n="0156002" resp="ihp" type="mod">虬【佛拓】，虯【史】</note><app n="0156002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虯</lem><rdg wit="【原】">虬</rdg></app>簷迥<note n="0156003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30930"/>＝構【史】</note><note n="0156003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30930"/>【佛拓】，構【史】</note><app n="0156003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">構</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30930"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0156a11" type="honorific"/>寶鐸依空。有類飛來。無殊
<lb ed="I" n="0156a12" type="honorific"/>湧出。當願福鍾
<lb ed="I" n="0156a13" type="honorific"/>七廟。卜世靡窮。聖主臨
<lb ed="I" n="0156a14" type="honorific"/>馭。弘茲萬壽。先王道洽群
<lb ed="I" n="0156a15" type="honorific"/>氓。先太妃德崇列閫。昊倉
<lb ed="I" n="0156a16" type="honorific"/><note n="0156004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30931"/>＝寡【史】</note><note n="0156004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30931"/>【佛拓】，寡【史】</note><app n="0156004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寡</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30931"/></rdg></app>惠。慈陰夙傾。思所以仰
<lb ed="I" n="0156a17" type="honorific"/>報　亡靈。祚覃遐<note n="0156005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𧛨＝裔【史】</note><note n="0156005" resp="ihp" type="mod">𧛨【佛拓】，裔【史】</note><app n="0156005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">裔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𧛨</rdg></app>。一切
<lb ed="I" n="0156a18" type="honorific"/>六道。彼岸咸登。金石是鐫。
<lb ed="I" n="0156a19" type="honorific"/>傳之不朽。標弟胡明達。
<lb ed="I" n="0156a20" type="honorific"/>定國寺主慧照
<lb ed="I" n="0156a21" type="honorific"/>□□□□□□主僧實</p>
